  <data key="d0">ALX Software Engineering Programme</data>
  <data key="d1">program</data>
  <data key="d2">The ALX Software Engineering Programme is a prominent engineering curriculum in Africa from which Daud Rahim graduated, contributing to his software foundation.&lt;SEP&gt;The ALX Software Engineering Programme is a rigorous 12-month engineering course completed by the individual.</data>
