  <data key="d0">Daud Rahim</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Daud Rahim is a full-stack developer in Ghana, building products and software for clients including enterprises and startups. His work spans web applications, SaaS products, and IoT systems.</data>
