<node id="Allied Ghana">
  <data key="d0">Allied Ghana</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Allied Ghana is one of the large enterprise clients of Daud Rahim for whom he builds full-stack web applications.&lt;SEP&gt;Allied Ghana is a company that became a client due to a referral from work completed for the KGL Group.&lt;SEP&gt;Allied Ghana, also known as Allied Oil, is a Ghanian fuel and lubricants company, and a client of Ri-Tech.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-81da984163c759bad699eb1f032dee3f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8e357f4aef23fb29f630d275ad3faaaa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67176d4f462a227eb0b8e63a6bd85927</data>
