  <data key="d2">Ri-Tech is a technology company co-founded in 2025, delivering projects across web development, mobile apps, networking, and branding in Ghana, and has served clients like KGL Group, Allied Ghana, Bonvas Tours, and St. Joseph's Catholic Hospital.</data>
